onto the Acropolis,

01:08:31.820 --> 01:08:35.149
seize the Acropolis,
make it your fortress,

01:08:35.149 --> 01:08:39.180
and proclaim yourself boss and
see if you can make it stick.

01:08:39.180 --> 01:08:43.658
